graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Backend[odh-dashboard Backend<br/>Node.js/Fastify<br/>Port 8080/TCP]
        Frontend[odh-dashboard Frontend<br/>React/TypeScript SPA]
        OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy Sidecar<br/>OpenShift OAuth<br/>Port 8443/TCP HTTPS]

        Frontend -->|serves static assets| Backend
        OAuthProxy -->|proxies & authenticates| Backend
    end

    subgraph "External Access"
        User[User Browser]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>reencrypt mode]
        Service[odh-dashboard Service<br/>ClusterIP 8443/TCP]
    end

    User -->|HTTPS/443| Route
    Route -->|HTTPS/8443| Service
    Service -->|HTTPS/8443| OAuthProxy

    subgraph "CRDs Managed"
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        HardwareProfile[HardwareProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
    end

    Backend -->|watches/manages| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|watches/manages| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|watches/manages| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|watches/manages| AcceleratorProfile
    Backend -->|watches/manages| HardwareProfile
    Backend -->|watches/manages| OdhQuickStart

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        ThanosQuerier[Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
        ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Backend -->|ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|OAuth 2.0 flow| OAuthServer
    Backend -->|metrics queries| ThanosQuerier
    Backend -->|image metadata| ImageRegistry

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInitialization]
        NotebooksController[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD]
        KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService CRD]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]
        ODHModelController[odh-model-controller<br/>ServingRuntime]
        NIMOperator[NIM Operator<br/>Account CRD]
    end

    Backend -->|watches/queries| ODHOperator
    Backend -->|creates/manages| NotebooksController
    Backend -->|queries status| KServe
    Backend -->|manages/queries| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|manages runtimes| ODHModelController
    Backend -->|manages accounts| NIMOperator

    subgraph "OpenShift Console Integration"
        ConsoleLink[ConsoleLink CRD<br/>Application Menu]
    end

    Backend -->|creates| ConsoleLink

